OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FGavin Robinson has said "it is clear"
OL,8,Fformer and current DUP members had
OL,9,Finformation about the conduct of child-
OL,10,Frapist Jeffrey Donaldson but did not
OL,11,Fshare it with the party.
OL,13,FHe insisted the party was not made
OL,14,Faware formally of any allegations
OL,15,Fabout the former leader's behaviour
OL,16,Fprior to his arrest in 2024.
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
