PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FThere have been growing calls from
OL,8,FStormont parties for a review set up
OL,9,Fby the DUP in the wake of the
OL,10,Fconviction to provide full
OL,11,Ftransparency over safeguarding issues.
OL,13,FDonaldson, 63, is in custody awaiting
OL,14,Fsentencing after being convicted of 18
OL,15,Fsexual offences against two women when
OL,16,Fthey were children.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FQuestions have been raised around
OL,8,Fwhether there was an awareness that he
OL,9,Fwas allegedly engaged in behaviour in
OL,10,Fhis private life that, although legal,
OL,11,Fwas at odds with positions he adopted
OL,12,Fpublicly.
OL,14,FMr Robinson said: "As a party we were
OL,15,Fnot aware of allegations that have
OL,16,Fsubsequently come to light.
OL,18,F"I may only have been leader of this
OL,19,Fparty for a short period of time, but
OL,20,FI am convinced that that is the case
OL,21,Ffor a longer period of time.
OL,26,@vD@SOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,F"It is clear there are a number of
OL,8,Findividuals, either former members of
OL,9,Fthe Democratic Unionist Party or
OL,10,Fcurrent, who did indicate publicly on
OL,11,FFriday that they had information that
OL,12,Fthey did not share, information that
OL,13,Fwas not reported through our
OL,14,Fappropriate channels and therefore
OL,15,Finformation about which we could do
OL,16,Fnothing formally.
OL,18,F"Whilst I say that with confidence, I
OL,19,Fam also clear it is not OK for that to
OL,20,Fcontinue to be the case.
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,F"I cannot countenance a circumstance
OL,8,For situation where I allow that to be
OL,9,Fthe case.
OL,11,F"That is why I and my deputy leader
OL,12,Fand senior party colleagues agreed on
OL,13,FFriday to institute a review; a review
OL,14,Fthat will be independent of our party,
OL,15,Fa review that will be conducted by an
OL,16,Findividual with impeccable credentials
OL,17,Fin child safeguarding, sexual
OL,18,Fexploitation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,F"I want them to establish if members
OL,8,Fof my party had information which they
OL,9,Fdid not share.
OL,11,F"I also want them to establish if
OL,12,Fthere are people within my party who
OL,13,Fcontinue to hold information which
OL,14,Fthey haven't yet felt (able to) share."
OL,16,FMr Robinson said he wanted the review
OL,17,Fto examine the party's safeguarding
OL,18,Fpolicies.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@WpmvD@_pnvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FBut he added: "If somebody doesn't
OL,8,Fcome forward and whistleblow, you
OL,9,Fcan't use the safeguarding policies.
OL,11,F"It is my job to set our standards and
OL,12,Fwhat we have heard over the last
OL,13,Fnumber of days falls well below the
OL,14,Fstandards that I hold and my
OL,15,Fcolleagues hold for our party.
OL,17,F"It is our job to make sure we are not
OL,18,Fturning a blind eye and that we deal
OL,19,Fwith the issues that we are in charge
OL,20,Fof."
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
