PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FBBC Spotlight reported that some
OL,8,Fsenior DUP figures were aware of
OL,9,Fanother woman, not linked to the sex
OL,10,Fabuse court case, who had raised
OL,11,Fconcerns about Donaldson's behaviour
OL,12,Fbut had not wished to make a formal
OL,13,Fcomplaint.
OL,15,FIn the programme, former North Antrim
OL,16,FMP Ian Paisley said the woman did not
OL,17,Fwant to make a formal complaint but he
OL,18,Fclaimed he told Edwin Poots, who was
OL,19,Fthen DUP leader and is now Stormont
OL,20,FSpeaker.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FAnnouncing an Assembly investigation
OL,8,Finto Donaldson's alleged inappropriate
OL,9,Fbehaviour at Stormont on Monday, Mr
OL,10,FPoots told MLAs he did nothing wrong
OL,11,Fin his handling of this allegation.
OL,13,FHe also urged the Civil Service and
OL,14,Fthe House of Commons to launch their
OL,15,Fown inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FSpotlight also reported that two
OL,8,Fsenior PSNI officers saw Donaldson
OL,9,Fentering a sauna in London that
OL,10,Fmarketed itself as a meeting place for
OL,11,Fgay men in 2006 ` despite the
OL,12,Fpolitician referring to homosexuality
OL,13,Fas "sinful" in the same year.
OL,15,FIn a statement on Friday, the DUP
OL,16,Fannounced a "specialised and detailed
OL,17,Findependent review into a number of
OL,18,Fissues arising" following Donaldson's
OL,19,Fconviction.
OL,26,@uD@DOUuD@KO]xD@MOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FMr Robinson said he had not yet spoken
OL,8,Fto Mr Poots about the issues raised in
OL,9,Fthe Spotlight programme.
OL,11,FThe Speaker has faced some calls to
OL,12,Fconsider stepping aside while the DUP
OL,13,Finvestigation is ongoing.
OL,15,FSinn Fein has said it intends to
OL,16,Fsubmit questions to the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Assembly on Monday, in
OL,18,Frelation to the claims aired about
OL,19,FDonaldson.
OL,26,@wD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
