OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FTUV leader Jim Allister said there was
OL,8,Fa "low level of confidence" in
OL,9,Fprevious internal DUP reviews
OL,11,FHe said: "A review can be of one of
OL,12,Ftwo types, it can be a stalling tactic
OL,13,Fsuch as we have seen in the past, self-
OL,14,Fserving and not revealing the truth.
OL,16,F"Or it can be thoroughgoing, hopefully
OL,17,Funfettered and capable of delivering
OL,18,Fthe truth."
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@[O]sD@JOUxD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
