PN,41913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1782838086
OL,3,CDUP leader says party members did not
OL,4,Cshare information over Donaldson's
OL,5,Cconduct
OL,7,FSDLP Stormont leader Matthew O'Toole
OL,8,Fsaid: "Clearly revelations over the
OL,9,Fpast few days have prompted further
OL,10,Fquestions which we need to answer here
OL,11,Fin the Northern Ireland Assembly
OL,13,F"We need to understand from the DUP
OL,14,Fwhether safeguarding processes were
OL,15,Fproperly followed following complaints
OL,16,Fto senior DUP members.
OL,18,F"We do need to hear the details of
OL,19,Fthose complaints and how they were
OL,20,Fdealt with, to ensure they were dealt
OL,21,Fwith properly."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
